title: Things to Bring Up in One-on-Ones

cells.data:
* When is rotation starting?
* Retro feels way too much like "team gives feedback, Luis defends himself" -- Luis doesn't need to always be the first one to speak when a card comes up.
* Please don't merge MY PRs or ignore my PR comments with a force merge.
* Don't rush to fix things. We almost merged a catastrophic change into Helmsman because of your hasty PR. All of your PRs are additive, never healing.
